{"tid":1550630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望聽日大家收一收手，星期一再開波。","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:40:21.000Z","uid":16086,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9b3c68fc58583181f5747a34a677d0b094510695","tid":1550630,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:55:18.000Z","msg":"聽日去領事館，都係向「外國表達聲音」為首要目的，<br />\n<br />\n所以聽日甚至連Gear都唔需要<br />\n<br />\n我唔希望夜晚見到新聞又係同黑警衝突，<br />\n而令領事館嘅聲音被遮蓋<br />\n<br />\n雖則有啲咩事都唔會割<br />\n但係希望大家會睇下情況再選擇要做啲咩"},{"pid":"ffa0c83a1af445e29b647a9fed943bb9012e543d","tid":1550630,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:55:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a28a0a297e4f8a772a65e7e9140b2a7fa0daf291","tid":1550630,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:57:13.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"5eb2350d6d594374a0db189368c1cd263c13a1a7","tid":1550630,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:58:00.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"110f300f0070134de2da82853d7058645fab64bc","tid":1550630,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0